{"tid":1346821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係想做野既人，入一入黎睇下","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:36.000Z","uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db4b71dec9529ca0eda2f719a554b63e6423f90f","tid":1346821,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"gear 個啲廢話唔講。<br />\n如果入元朗，最好有遊行，和理非照常行。<br />\n勇武手足唔好跟遊行路線行，趁警力分散之後，做下野。<br />\n<br />\n最好條路線有幾長得咁長，可以肯定警犬一定重兵擺晒唔同鄉黑地點，到時你去到又係成肚氣，但係佢無可能保晒咁多地方，就算得都唔會多警察，到時有得打狗又有得打鄉黑。<br />\n<br />\n依家根本就人少警察就行開，等狗打你，人多警察就上黎開槍。<br />\n<br />\n愚見，有無人討論下。"},{"pid":"1b5d7a3f5ac54f2062b15f04f3328601dde4c36d","tid":1346821,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"be water 啦"},{"pid":"965c2f33dc945e2a5be4015a5e7817b6bf1ec4aa","tid":1346821,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"講真，鄉黑得幾百人實夠打，問題係點打"},{"pid":"4252fcc40e42ff0fcccd2a5ee064bd2df595fbbc","tid":1346821,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2450327688378864?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2450327688378864%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=9aa672a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2450327688378864?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n0&rsquo;22 開始，香港人醒未？"}]}